author: fielding
msg: M_INVALID needs a value within the scope of METHODS so that unknown
methods can be access controlled. MMP must be bumped because this may
break binary compatibility for third-party modules.

author: coar
msg: Add PassAllEnv to make all of the server's environment variables
available to CGIs and SSIs within the directive's scope.  NOT
recommended for general use, but eases the transition for IBM's
